module.name: status.screen.first_description_end_free_trial
Lengow: Your free 15-day trial period on Lengow has now expired. We know that it is sad news, but the best is yet to come! We sincerely hope Lengow has helped you improve your business.

module.name: status.screen.second_description_end_free_trial
Lengow: Your account will be suspended until you purchase a new subscription. All existing distributions and importations will also be suspended.

module.name: status.screen.third_description_end_free_trial
Lengow: Don't forget that trial accounts are deleted 30 days after the end of the trial period. Make sure to subscribe so you do not lose the work you've done building channels.

module.name: status.screen.subtitle_bad_payer
Lengow: Your account has been temporarily shut down

module.name: status.screen.first_description_bad_payer
Lengow: We are sorry to inform you that we have had to limit access to your account temporarily because the automatic payment of your subscription failed.

module.name: status.screen.second_description_bad_payer
Lengow: The posting of your catalogue has been suspended. We strongly suggest that you get in touch with us at

module.name: status.screen.third_description_bad_payer
Lengow: We hope to work with you again in the near future.

module.name: status.screen.upgrade_account_button
